lead_paragraph: Kevin Chappell, a three times runner-up this season, has another chance to earn his maiden PGA Tour win after moving into a one-shot lead over Jimmy Walker and Paul Casey after two rounds of the Deutsche Bank Championship in Massachusetts on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Chappell Heads Walker, Casey by One at Boston TPC
